## 📋 标准来源

### 核心标准

- **[The System Design Primer](https://github.com/donnemartin/system-design-primer)** - 系统设计入门
- **[AWS Well-Architected Framework](https://aws.amazon.com/architecture/well-architected/)** - AWS 架构框架
- **[Google Cloud Architecture](https://cloud.google.com/architecture)** - Google 云架构
- **[Microsoft Azure Architecture](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/architecture/)** - Microsoft Azure 架构

### 行业最佳实践

- **Microservices Architecture** - 微服务架构
- **Event-Driven Architecture** - 事件驱动架构
- **Service Mesh** - 服务网格
- **Domain-Driven Design (DDD)** - 领域驱动设计

